1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:00,933
welcome back

2
00:00:00,933 --> 00:00:05,666
since it has now been a long time since when we moved to our new base

3
00:00:05,666 --> 00:00:09,333
I think it's a good idea to go pay a visit to the old one

4
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:11,333
and while doing some cleaning

5
00:00:11,333 --> 00:00:13,300
we bumped into a bookshelf

6
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:15,733
making a particular book fall out of it

7
00:00:16,033 --> 00:00:17,233
upon inspection

8
00:00:17,233 --> 00:00:21,333
it looks like some ancient wizardry Tome we didn't knew we had

9
00:00:21,666 --> 00:00:23,533
but it caught our attention

10
00:00:23,733 --> 00:00:25,666
and out of curiosity

11
00:00:25,666 --> 00:00:29,233
we wanted to try following some of its weird rituals

12
00:00:29,266 --> 00:00:33,700
the first one consist of placing a rudimentary pen on a couple of tables

13
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,700
to merge those in a single table

14
00:00:35,933 --> 00:00:39,900
the second one asks us to put a green tablecloth on another table

15
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:44,100
and now we are supposed to do some research on the bigger table

16
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:48,233
but it looks like we are not knowledgeable enough in the art of magic

17
00:00:48,233 --> 00:00:52,800
so we made a lens capable of revealing us the nature of the things around us

18
00:00:53,066 --> 00:00:55,733
and thus we start our magical research

19
00:00:55,733 --> 00:00:59,000
to find out what the world around us is made out of

20
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,066
turns out that

21
00:01:00,066 --> 00:01:07,133
basically everything is actually a combination of compounds of six primal aspects which compose all of the atoms

22
00:01:07,133 --> 00:01:12,000
after an exhaustive research of all the peculiarities this world has to show us

23
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,733
we are finally ready to try and do some research

24
00:01:14,733 --> 00:01:17,633
to better understand how things connect together

25
00:01:17,633 --> 00:01:21,600
forming theories which we can use for our magic experiments

26
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:25,400
and now it is time to get all absorbed into our studies

27
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,700
to unlock all of the knowledge that a common folk can have

28
00:01:28,733 --> 00:01:31,933
and doing all of that research made us quite hungry

29
00:01:31,933 --> 00:01:33,466
so we gather some shrooms

30
00:01:33,466 --> 00:01:36,866
and use our newly acquired magic powers to get a cauldron

31
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:41,866
we are going to make a nice stew out of wheat, stone and magic shrooms

32
00:01:42,033 --> 00:01:45,433
and it looks like somez grew out of it

33
00:01:45,733 --> 00:01:48,266
we decide to take those back to our base

34
00:01:48,266 --> 00:01:49,933
and cultivate those

35
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:51,466
and to help the growth

36
00:01:51,466 --> 00:01:53,733
we can use an ultimate time anomaly

37
00:01:53,933 --> 00:01:55,633
once they are fully grown

38
00:01:55,633 --> 00:01:58,066
we can harvest those to drop spores

39
00:01:58,066 --> 00:02:02,433
that we can collect and convert into magic power with the help of our broom

40
00:02:02,633 --> 00:02:07,600
we can use that magic power in our green clothed table to craft a proper magic wand

41
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,400
to do some better magic

42
00:02:09,666 --> 00:02:13,266
this wand will carry twice the power of our old broom

43
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:18,100
which also means that we have to cultivate twice as many shrooms

44
00:02:18,333 --> 00:02:20,066
since that is too annoying

45
00:02:20,066 --> 00:02:22,933
we shall use that power to find a solution

46
00:02:23,433 --> 00:02:25,933
we start by making a better magic table

47
00:02:25,933 --> 00:02:29,533
one that can easily pull the crafting items from ae2

48
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:34,133
which we use to craft the tools for fixing our issues with Mana

49
00:02:34,133 --> 00:02:35,633
also knows as Vis

50
00:02:36,266 --> 00:02:38,500
now we only need a source of Vis

51
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,233
luckily

52
00:02:39,233 --> 00:02:44,233
we can use all the coins we have stocked up to buy a node from the quest book

53
00:02:45,066 --> 00:02:46,766
we free it from its container

54
00:02:46,766 --> 00:02:49,800
and drop it inside its new containment glass

55
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,333
now

56
00:02:50,333 --> 00:02:53,900
we slowly tame it into a nice usable source of power

57
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,700
which we can check with our new goggles

58
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:59,400
finally to use its power

59
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,033
we place a vis relay nearby

60
00:03:01,033 --> 00:03:03,433
and connect it to our crafting table

61
00:03:04,033 --> 00:03:04,866
and with that

62
00:03:04,866 --> 00:03:07,466
we are getting free passive magic power

63
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:11,733
which we can use to craft a new collection of crystals

64
00:03:12,133 --> 00:03:13,400
but to do things

65
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,933
we also need some salis mundus

66
00:03:16,033 --> 00:03:18,733
which we can cook into balanced shards

67
00:03:18,733 --> 00:03:22,100
and ignore the random purple fumes coming out of our cauldron

68
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:25,866
they are just a new decoration for our old base

69
00:03:26,133 --> 00:03:28,800
and we also gather some Silverwood Trees

70
00:03:28,933 --> 00:03:30,666
just a few logs

71
00:03:31,233 --> 00:03:33,133
that was to craft some Alembics

72
00:03:33,133 --> 00:03:36,266
which will go on top of our new essentia furnace

73
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,033
with that

74
00:03:37,033 --> 00:03:40,666
we can break down anything into its essentia components

75
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:43,433
the essentia will be extracted by the alembic

76
00:03:43,433 --> 00:03:47,600
which with the help of pipes will output into jars

77
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,000
this essentia can be used with phials in a crucible

78
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,933
but what we are going to do next

79
00:03:52,933 --> 00:03:55,866
is something slightly bigger and more complex

80
00:03:55,866 --> 00:03:56,633
infusion

81
00:03:57,066 --> 00:03:58,733
after building a big altar

82
00:03:58,833 --> 00:04:01,466
we place the required essentia nearby

83
00:04:01,466 --> 00:04:05,066
then after placing the correct items on the pedestals

84
00:04:05,066 --> 00:04:06,866
we can start the process

85
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,933
this is a really slow process

86
00:04:08,933 --> 00:04:11,433
and we have to place a lot of stabilizer things

87
00:04:11,433 --> 00:04:15,900
such as the quicksilver blocks on the flooring to stabilize the process

88
00:04:16,133 --> 00:04:16,800
however

89
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:20,700
the best way of doing that is by using some help from our technology

90
00:04:20,733 --> 00:04:22,866
by turning on our time anomaly

91
00:04:22,866 --> 00:04:27,300
the process will finish before its animation even manages to complete

92
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,100
and our first infused thing

93
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:33,700
is something that will let our technology help even further with our magic things

94
00:04:33,933 --> 00:04:36,033
we are indeed in the digital era

95
00:04:36,033 --> 00:04:40,666
there is no longer need to use those barbaric phials to manage our essentia

96
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,733
we can use DG(digital) essentia

97
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:47,866
now we can easily manage huge amounts of essentia from our AE2 network

98
00:04:48,233 --> 00:04:51,133
now we have to get rid of the barbaric crucible

99
00:04:51,233 --> 00:04:54,300
to do so we craft an essentia provider

100
00:04:55,033 --> 00:04:58,933
we place it next to an alchemical construct on top of a crucible

101
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:01,666
now we only have to input the finishing item

102
00:05:01,666 --> 00:05:03,200
and select the recipe

103
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:06,300
and there we have our clean crucible management

104
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,633
the next thing we have to manage better is our vis

105
00:05:09,833 --> 00:05:12,233
to do so we want a better wand

106
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:14,500
however to get the good ones

107
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:16,133
we are going to need some more on essentia

108
00:05:16,133 --> 00:05:18,733
which is super annoying to get

109
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,100
or maybe not

110
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:22,433
we just have to catch a wisp

111
00:05:22,433 --> 00:05:25,833
then turn it into a spawner and put it in our mob farm

112
00:05:26,533 --> 00:05:30,733
that will give us all kinds of essentia always with extra auram

113
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,666
we also get auram with extra auram

114
00:05:34,466 --> 00:05:37,000
after breaking down the essence into essentia

115
00:05:37,033 --> 00:05:39,000
we can craft our new wand core

116
00:05:39,633 --> 00:05:40,300
however

117
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:43,300
while that core will allow for higher vis capacity

118
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:46,766
we should also try to get a better discount on the usage

119
00:05:46,766 --> 00:05:49,000
but caps are not enough

120
00:05:49,133 --> 00:05:50,300
we shall get a machine

121
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:55,300
that will help us craft the materials for some dresses more appropriate for the occasion

122
00:05:56,233 --> 00:05:58,600
and after some textile work

123
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:01,600
we managed to make a new set of fashionable clothing

124
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:04,633
however that was not enough

125
00:06:04,733 --> 00:06:06,833
our wand carry is 120 vis

126
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:10,433
and even with our current discount

127
00:06:10,433 --> 00:06:13,733
we need 120.1 for a better wand

128
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:16,633
we need better dresses

129
00:06:16,733 --> 00:06:17,233
luckily

130
00:06:17,233 --> 00:06:21,633
our magic book has a whole section dedicated only to shoes

131
00:06:22,333 --> 00:06:24,633
but this is not a retail store book

132
00:06:24,633 --> 00:06:26,800
we have to do some sketchy rituals

133
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,700
to get our new accessories

134
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:32,200
and sometimes stuff goes wrong

135
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:35,433
we had forgotten some of the required essentia

136
00:06:36,233 --> 00:06:37,000
to fix that

137
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,033
we can make an infusion essentia provider

138
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:44,733
that thing will let our infusion process work with DG essentia

139
00:06:44,733 --> 00:06:47,600
no more need for those ugly jars

140
00:06:48,133 --> 00:06:51,333
and there we have a new pair of nice looking goggles

141
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:55,066
however those don't match well with our shoes

142
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:57,800
and after looking at the shoes section

143
00:06:57,833 --> 00:07:01,033
we couldn't find anything that fits well with our new goggles

144
00:07:01,033 --> 00:07:05,133
so we instead moved to the electro magic stuff

145
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:09,000
this is forbidden stuff that only VIPs can use

146
00:07:09,433 --> 00:07:11,300
now that we are fashionable enough

147
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:12,900
we can get a better wand

148
00:07:13,466 --> 00:07:15,900
which we quickly upgrade twice

149
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:18,533
but we are not satisfied yet

150
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:19,633
however

151
00:07:19,633 --> 00:07:20,866
to make a better wand

152
00:07:20,866 --> 00:07:22,733
we need to use a different path

153
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,200
or to dress better

154
00:07:24,433 --> 00:07:28,033
however while we could do more cool electro magic tools

155
00:07:28,033 --> 00:07:31,266
we should probably go into a proper magician outfit

156
00:07:31,466 --> 00:07:34,933
but that requires us to do definitely too much research

157
00:07:35,533 --> 00:07:38,000
luckily technology can help there too

158
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,633
we can craft a machine

159
00:07:39,633 --> 00:07:43,600
that will use electricity and node power to complete researches for us

160
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,133
all we have to do is input a research

161
00:07:46,133 --> 00:07:47,933
and take out the discovery

162
00:07:48,233 --> 00:07:48,900
with that

163
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:51,700
we can now research everything we can click on

164
00:07:51,933 --> 00:07:52,666
however

165
00:07:52,666 --> 00:07:57,433
doing so much research is actually destroying the node this machine uses

166
00:07:57,533 --> 00:08:02,300
so we have to go find and bring back home a bunch of new nodes to do more research

167
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:06,000
which might takes more time than manually doing said research

168
00:08:06,233 --> 00:08:10,433
also the weak nodes we find in nature won't last much

169
00:08:10,666 --> 00:08:11,266
thus

170
00:08:11,266 --> 00:08:14,866
we shall find a way of artificially creating new nodes

171
00:08:15,033 --> 00:08:18,100
we start by making an unattuned node matrix

172
00:08:18,733 --> 00:08:22,433
then we feed it all the useless essentia we have lying around

173
00:08:22,733 --> 00:08:25,466
finally we infuse it into a node

174
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,333
however

175
00:08:26,333 --> 00:08:29,500
that process is starting to take up too much essentia

176
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:32,533
so we have to find a better way of melting items

177
00:08:32,666 --> 00:08:36,133
and the large essentia smelter seems perfect for the job

178
00:08:36,333 --> 00:08:37,100
however

179
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:40,100
we miss some of the knowledge required to craft it

180
00:08:40,533 --> 00:08:43,200
that knowledge is in a weird page of the magic book

181
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,266
that just appeared out of nowhere

182
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:49,300
and everything inside it looks spooky and seems to be taboo

183
00:08:49,733 --> 00:08:52,600
but we decide to follow those weird rituals

184
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,000
and join the cult

185
00:08:54,133 --> 00:08:56,833
and we are offered a nice looking dark armor

186
00:08:57,033 --> 00:08:59,633
but I sustain that the white one is better

187
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,600
and that caused an argument with the cult leader who didn't agree

188
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:05,800
so we proved our superiority

189
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,000
and then jailed him

190
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:10,733
until he gave us the secret book with all the taboo rituals

191
00:09:10,933 --> 00:09:14,066
however the more we go down that taboo stuff

192
00:09:14,066 --> 00:09:17,233
the more weird things start to happen around us

193
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:20,333
sometimes we are followed by spiders

194
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:22,333
others by Arshog

195
00:09:22,866 --> 00:09:25,866
and other times we are followed by ourselves

196
00:09:26,233 --> 00:09:28,866
this is probably caused by too much work

197
00:09:28,866 --> 00:09:32,000
so we shall take a quick break in our new spa

198
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,833
after our quick break

199
00:09:33,833 --> 00:09:36,333
it's time to go back to our studies

200
00:09:36,433 --> 00:09:38,466
which keep getting more spooky

201
00:09:38,633 --> 00:09:41,200
but we are now too deep in the rabbit hole

202
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,233
so the only way is forward

203
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:46,533
and the next task our books are telling us to do

204
00:09:46,533 --> 00:09:49,300
is to create a black hole at one of the cursed altars

205
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:51,600
we had seen laying around on the map

206
00:09:52,633 --> 00:09:54,000
following that path

207
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
we have reached the Dark Realm

208
00:09:57,333 --> 00:10:00,700
and after wandering in this labyrinth for a while

209
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:02,533
we have found a weird door

210
00:10:03,433 --> 00:10:06,500
luckily the key was lying in a room close by

211
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:09,633
with just a couple of old weak ghosts protecting it

212
00:10:10,433 --> 00:10:12,633
and our magnet quickly grabbed it

213
00:10:13,233 --> 00:10:16,400
with that key we can now open the ancient door

214
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:24,633
and what we find behind is someone who is capable to take some of our carbon tipped vanadium steel sharpened auto repair bolts

215
00:10:25,033 --> 00:10:27,200
he also managed to make us hungry

216
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,933
and deal us some damage

217
00:10:28,933 --> 00:10:30,833
so we turn on our quantum shield

218
00:10:30,833 --> 00:10:36,933
while we look for some tasty food in our AE2 terminal that can work wirelessly up to this place

219
00:10:37,433 --> 00:10:39,000
once we are well fed

220
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,733
we can take down that annoying bug

221
00:10:40,733 --> 00:10:44,233
without even bothering to pick up a sword from our backpack

222
00:10:44,866 --> 00:10:49,333
and he left us the thing we were missing for our upgraded essentia smelting

223
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:53,633
however since we have only one of these pearls

224
00:10:53,633 --> 00:10:56,666
we shall plant it on an island where the air is fresh

225
00:10:57,533 --> 00:11:00,900
then we speed up the growth with some time anomalies

226
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:03,200
and it looks like it's growing so fast

227
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:07,233
that our crop matron can't hydrate and fertilizer it fast enough

228
00:11:09,033 --> 00:11:14,133
not even a UV crop manager can keep up with the hunger of our accelerated crop

229
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,433
and it was then that

230
00:11:16,433 --> 00:11:19,600
the ghosts came to remind us to take a break from our farming

231
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,000
and have a nice bath

232
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:25,733
and we came back just in time to see our pearl bloom

233
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:31,400
and we use that to craft the missing piece for our essentia smelter

234
00:11:32,033 --> 00:11:34,466
this crafting has some instability

235
00:11:34,466 --> 00:11:40,133
so we add a bunch of blocks and decorations to our altar to increase the stability

236
00:11:40,866 --> 00:11:41,633
and thus

237
00:11:41,633 --> 00:11:47,033
we managed to keep the Runic matrix inside its area while we crafted the new machine

238
00:11:47,833 --> 00:11:49,866
but that was just the controller

239
00:11:50,033 --> 00:11:51,733
we need more parts

240
00:11:52,433 --> 00:11:56,133
the rest of the structure requires about 20 more infusions

241
00:11:56,133 --> 00:11:58,866
and since we are in the industrial age

242
00:11:58,866 --> 00:12:02,200
we shall not do infusions like barbarians

243
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:06,233
Steve's factory manager can manage factories

244
00:12:06,233 --> 00:12:09,533
I guess it can also manage ancient rituals

245
00:12:10,666 --> 00:12:13,833
we could do a nice tutorial on how to set this thing up

246
00:12:13,833 --> 00:12:16,866
but I think it does not fit properly in our adventure

247
00:12:16,866 --> 00:12:18,933
so if you want a tutorial

248
00:12:18,933 --> 00:12:21,000
remind me in the comments

249
00:12:22,900 --> 00:12:25,866
anyways after a long trial and error session

250
00:12:25,866 --> 00:12:30,200
we managed to get our infusion to work on a 2 second timer delay

251
00:12:31,066 --> 00:12:33,933
which for the way this program is made

252
00:12:33,933 --> 00:12:36,733
means one infusion every 4 seconds

253
00:12:37,733 --> 00:12:39,900
but it's not even a complete setup

254
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:42,666
since we still have to manually manage essentia

255
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:45,066
even though there are better options

256
00:12:46,266 --> 00:12:49,866
and we should also make sure the altar is stable enough

257
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:54,666
and that setup was good enough to complete our new essentia smelter

258
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,866
which works at a decent speed

259
00:12:57,866 --> 00:12:59,666
but makes quite some flux

260
00:13:00,733 --> 00:13:03,033
but we can upgrade it in many ways

261
00:13:03,033 --> 00:13:05,066
until it satisfies us

262
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,333
now we just have to do a lot of clicking

263
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:11,866
and I think that might be giving us some warp

264
00:13:12,533 --> 00:13:16,100
anyways once we are too annoyed by all the clicking

265
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:18,300
we can turn that thing into a node

266
00:13:18,633 --> 00:13:22,400
that is going to take four times more essentia than what we threw in

267
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:29,233
meaning that even with a 256 speedup it will still take some time to complete

268
00:13:29,666 --> 00:13:33,800
but at least in that phase we can just sit and watch

269
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,400
until we finally get a new node

270
00:13:36,733 --> 00:13:39,133
which we shall use for research

271
00:13:39,633 --> 00:13:42,433
that node is going to be used up quite fast

272
00:13:42,433 --> 00:13:47,100
but I think it's still easier to make than manually doing all of these researches

273
00:13:47,233 --> 00:13:49,600
also if we were to go slower

274
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,033
there might be ways to restore the node

275
00:13:52,300 --> 00:13:55,266
and that is what was left after all that research

276
00:13:55,433 --> 00:13:56,433
by the way

277
00:13:56,433 --> 00:13:59,733
there's another way to make nodes with millions of aspects

278
00:13:59,733 --> 00:14:01,733
but I don't know how it works

279
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:06,200
also I think the process we just did gave me a little bit of warp

280
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:09,666
so I think it is a good time to get a good cleaning

281
00:14:09,833 --> 00:14:10,800
to do so

282
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:12,633
all we need is a pure tear

283
00:14:13,033 --> 00:14:16,133
or maybe we can upgrade it into a passive accessory

284
00:14:16,533 --> 00:14:19,866
that thing is going to slowly remove all of our warp

285
00:14:20,066 --> 00:14:22,200
let's see how fast it is

286
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,600
and in half of a Minecraft day

287
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,500
it removed none of our permanent warp

288
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,066
and some of the normal one

289
00:14:37,466 --> 00:14:41,500
since that thing was supposed to be faster when you have more warp

290
00:14:41,533 --> 00:14:43,733
I guess it will take too much time

291
00:14:43,733 --> 00:14:45,466
so let's just use it here

292
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:49,833
that gave us all sorts of effects for half an hour

293
00:14:49,833 --> 00:14:53,800
tired of waiting with no idea of how much longer that would have lasted

294
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:56,900
we just decided to take the faster approach

295
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:59,066
and with our luck

296
00:14:59,066 --> 00:15:02,400
a couple of withers spawned exactly on the last moment

297
00:15:02,533 --> 00:15:04,733
luckily that didn't bother us

298
00:15:04,733 --> 00:15:06,733
so we could safely retrieve our stuff

299
00:15:06,733 --> 00:15:08,266
and go back to work

300
00:15:08,566 --> 00:15:12,300
and now you might be wondering why we went through all of that

301
00:15:12,666 --> 00:15:13,233
well

302
00:15:13,233 --> 00:15:16,833
there are many quality of life things gated by Thaumcraft

303
00:15:16,933 --> 00:15:20,200
the first one is that we need the essentia wireless terminal

304
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,233
to get the universal terminal

305
00:15:22,466 --> 00:15:26,300
which will allow us to do a lot of AE2 interactions from anywhere

306
00:15:26,833 --> 00:15:29,033
next with a rainbow cacti

307
00:15:29,033 --> 00:15:31,533
we can craft the infinite spray can

308
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:35,333
also we can now craft hearth canisters

309
00:15:35,333 --> 00:15:36,700
so that we can find out

310
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:39,266
what are the next colors for our health bar

311
00:15:39,666 --> 00:15:44,433
finally some magical vanilla items require thaumcraft to be crafted

312
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:47,300
those items are required to some rituals

313
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:49,300
to activate an ancient sigil

314
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:55,033
and you may wonder why we are going through the siege for those ancient broken things

315
00:15:55,133 --> 00:15:57,233
well the answer is simple

316
00:15:57,233 --> 00:15:58,933
after so many years

317
00:15:58,933 --> 00:16:03,266
we want to put an answer to one of the oldest philosophical questions

318
00:16:03,466 --> 00:16:05,600
well the answer is simple

319
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,266
after so many years

320
00:16:07,266 --> 00:16:11,700
we want to find a solution for one of the oldest mathematical questions

321
00:16:11,833 --> 00:16:14,500
what does iron divided by diamond do

322
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:17,800
and it seems the answer is in Schrödinger cat

323
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,233
so what's the lesson today

324
00:16:20,466 --> 00:16:21,133
yeah

325
00:16:21,133 --> 00:16:24,766
always AE2 craft things while you mess around

326
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:00,933
欢迎回来！

327
00:00:00,933 --> 00:00:05,666
乔迁新居已许久

328
00:00:05,666 --> 00:00:09,333
何不予旧宅一访

329
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:11,333
在我们打扫的时候

330
00:00:11,333 --> 00:00:13,300
不慎撞到了一个书架

331
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:15,733
而这让一本书从中掉出

332
00:00:16,033 --> 00:00:17,233
经检查

333
00:00:17,233 --> 00:00:21,333
看起来像是某本未知的古代魔法书

334
00:00:21,666 --> 00:00:23,533
它引起了我们的注意

335
00:00:23,733 --> 00:00:25,666
出于好奇

336
00:00:25,666 --> 00:00:29,233
我们想试着进行书中的奇怪的仪式

337
00:00:29,266 --> 00:00:33,700
首先是在书桌上放上一支普通的笔

338
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,700
来把桌子合并起来

339
00:00:35,933 --> 00:00:39,900
然后是在另一张桌子上放一块绿色桌布

340
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:44,100
现在我们可以在更大的桌子上做些研究

341
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:48,233
但看起来我们的魔法技艺还不够

342
00:00:48,233 --> 00:00:50,400
所以我们做了一个魔导透镜

343
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:52,800
用来揭示周围事物的本质

344
00:00:53,066 --> 00:00:55,733
所以我们开始魔法研究

345
00:00:55,733 --> 00:00:59,000
去探究世界之本源

346
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,033
事实证明

347
00:01:00,033 --> 00:01:03,433
基本上所有物质都由原子化合

348
00:01:03,433 --> 00:01:07,133
而原子由六大基本元素组合而成

349
00:01:07,133 --> 00:01:12,000
在对这个世界的所有特殊性进行了详尽的调查之后

350
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:14,733
我们终于准备好进行一些研究

351
00:01:14,733 --> 00:01:17,633
来更好地了解各个事物之间的联系

352
00:01:17,633 --> 00:01:21,600
产生用于魔法研究的理论

353
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:25,400
现在是时候沉入学海了

354
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,700
来解锁一介凡人可获得的所有知识

355
00:01:28,733 --> 00:01:31,933
做了这么多研究让我们饥肠辘辘

356
00:01:31,933 --> 00:01:33,466
所以收集好一些蘑菇

357
00:01:33,466 --> 00:01:36,866
用最近取得的魔法力量获得坩埚

358
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:41,866
我们用小麦、石头和魔法蘑菇做一道美味炖菜

359
00:01:42,033 --> 00:01:45,433
看起来是做出了始源蘑菇

360
00:01:45,733 --> 00:01:48,266
我们决定把它们带回基地

361
00:01:48,266 --> 00:01:49,933
并且培养它们

362
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:51,466
想让它们长快点

363
00:01:51,466 --> 00:01:53,733
我们可以利用世界加速器

364
00:01:53,933 --> 00:01:55,633
一旦它们完全长大

365
00:01:55,633 --> 00:01:58,066
收获它们会产生孢子

366
00:01:58,066 --> 00:02:00,100
在法杖的帮助下

367
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:02,433
孢子将转化为魔力

368
00:02:02,633 --> 00:02:04,133
我们用那些魔力

369
00:02:04,133 --> 00:02:07,600
在奥数工作台上制作一根合适的魔杖

370
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,400
来施展更好的魔法

371
00:02:09,666 --> 00:02:13,266
这根魔杖的容量是之前的两倍

372
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:18,100
这也意味着种两倍的蘑菇

373
00:02:18,333 --> 00:02:20,066
这太烦人了

374
00:02:20,066 --> 00:02:22,933
我们将利用法杖的力量找到解决办法

375
00:02:23,433 --> 00:02:25,933
从制作更好的魔法桌开始

376
00:02:25,933 --> 00:02:29,533
它可以直接从 AE 里拉取物品

377
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:34,133
我们用它来制作解决法力问题的工具

378
00:02:34,133 --> 00:02:35,633
魔力也被称为 Vis

379
00:02:36,266 --> 00:02:38,500
现在我们只需要解决各类 Vis 的来源

380
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,233
幸运地

381
00:02:39,233 --> 00:02:41,933
我们可以使用囤积的所有硬币

382
00:02:41,933 --> 00:02:44,233
从任务书中购买一个节点

383
00:02:45,066 --> 00:02:46,766
我们把它从容器中释放出来

384
00:02:46,766 --> 00:02:49,800
放入新的容器玻璃中

385
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,333
现在

386
00:02:50,333 --> 00:02:53,900
慢慢地把它驯服成一个优秀的 Vis 来源

387
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,700
我们可以用新护目镜检查一下

388
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:59,400
要使用它的魔力

389
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,033
我们在附近放置一个 Vis 中继器

390
00:03:01,033 --> 00:03:03,433
并将其连接到工作台

391
00:03:04,033 --> 00:03:04,866
有了这个

392
00:03:04,866 --> 00:03:07,466
我们正在获得免费的被动魔力

393
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:11,733
我们用它制作一系列魔晶

394
00:03:12,133 --> 00:03:13,400
如果要真正做事

395
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,933
我们还需要一些世界盐

396
00:03:16,033 --> 00:03:18,733
它可以被煮成平衡碎片

397
00:03:18,733 --> 00:03:22,100
忽略从大锅里随机冒出来的紫色烟雾

398
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:25,866
它们只是我们旧基地的新装饰

399
00:03:26,133 --> 00:03:28,800
我们还收集了一些银木

400
00:03:28,933 --> 00:03:30,666
就几根木头

401
00:03:31,233 --> 00:03:33,133
来制作一些蒸馏器

402
00:03:33,133 --> 00:03:36,266
放在新的源质炉子上

403
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,033
有了那个

404
00:03:37,033 --> 00:03:40,666
我们可以把任何东西分解成它的基本源质

405
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:43,433
源质将由蒸馏器提取

406
00:03:43,433 --> 00:03:45,366
在管道的帮助下

407
00:03:45,366 --> 00:03:47,600
输出到罐子里

408
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,000
可以把坩埚里的源质导入安瓿使用

409
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,933
但是我们接下来要做的

410
00:03:52,933 --> 00:03:55,866
是更大更复杂一些的东西

411
00:03:55,866 --> 00:03:56,633
注魔

412
00:03:57,066 --> 00:03:58,733
建好大祭坛后

413
00:03:58,833 --> 00:04:01,466
我们将所需的源质放在附近

414
00:04:01,466 --> 00:04:05,066
在把正确的物品放在基座上后

415
00:04:05,066 --> 00:04:06,866
便可以开始了

416
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,933
这是一个非常缓慢的过程

417
00:04:08,933 --> 00:04:11,433
我们必须放置很多稳定物

418
00:04:11,433 --> 00:04:15,900
例如地板上的水银块以稳定过程

419
00:04:16,133 --> 00:04:16,800
然而

420
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:20,700
解决此问题的最佳方法是求助于科技

421
00:04:20,733 --> 00:04:22,866
通过开启世界加速器

422
00:04:22,866 --> 00:04:27,300
注魔过程在动画完成前就能结束

423
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,100
我们第一个注魔物

424
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:33,700
能让科技更进一步帮助我们

425
00:04:33,933 --> 00:04:36,033
我们本就处于数字时代

426
00:04:36,033 --> 00:04:40,666
不再需要使用那些野蛮的安瓿来管理源质

427
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,733
我们可以使用数字源质

428
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:47,866
现在可以轻松地在 AE 中管理大量源质了

429
00:04:48,233 --> 00:04:51,133
现在我们要摆脱野蛮的坩埚

430
00:04:51,233 --> 00:04:54,300
为此，我们制作了一个源质提供器

431
00:04:55,033 --> 00:04:58,933
我们把它放在坩埚顶部的炼金术构造旁边

432
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:01,666
现在我们只需要输入完成物

433
00:05:01,666 --> 00:05:03,200
并选择对应配方

434
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:06,300
这就是我们整洁的坩埚自动化

435
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,633
接下来我们优化 Vis

436
00:05:09,833 --> 00:05:12,233
为此，我们需要一根更好的魔杖

437
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:14,500
然而，为了做一根

438
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:16,133
我们需要更多的源质

439
00:05:16,133 --> 00:05:18,733
这太烦人了

440
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,100
并非

441
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:22,433
我们只要抓住一只精灵

442
00:05:22,433 --> 00:05:25,833
把它变成刷怪蛋放在工业屠宰场里

443
00:05:26,533 --> 00:05:30,733
那会产出全部种类的源质以及灵气

444
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,666
我们还获得了带有额外灵气的天域之华

445
00:05:34,466 --> 00:05:37,000
将天域之华分解成源质后

446
00:05:37,033 --> 00:05:39,000
我们可以制作新的杖芯

447
00:05:39,633 --> 00:05:40,300
虽然说

448
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:43,300
此核心允许更高的 Vis 容量

449
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:46,766
但我们也要有高的减免

450
00:05:46,766 --> 00:05:49,000
只有杖端是不够的

451
00:05:49,133 --> 00:05:50,300
我们应该做一台机器

452
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:55,300
来做更合适魔法的服装的所需材料

453
00:05:56,233 --> 00:05:58,600
在一些纺织工作之后

454
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:01,600
我们做出了一套新的时尚服装

455
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:04,633
然而，这还不够

456
00:06:04,733 --> 00:06:06,833
我们法杖可携带 120 Vis

457
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:10,433
即使按照目前减免来算

458
00:06:10,433 --> 00:06:13,733
也需要 120.1 的 Vis 来做更好的魔杖

459
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:16,633
我们需要更好的衣服

460
00:06:16,733 --> 00:06:17,233
幸运地

461
00:06:17,233 --> 00:06:21,633
我们的魔法书有一整节专门介绍鞋子

462
00:06:22,333 --> 00:06:24,633
但这不是零售店的书

463
00:06:24,633 --> 00:06:26,800
我们得做些粗糙的仪式

464
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,700
来获取我们的新配饰

465
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:32,200
有时事情会出错

466
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:35,433
我们忘记了一些必要的源质

467
00:06:36,233 --> 00:06:37,000
想解决这个问题

468
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,033
我们可以做一个注魔供应器

469
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:44,733
这可以让注魔自动使用数字源质

470
00:06:44,733 --> 00:06:47,600
不再需要那些丑陋的罐子了

471
00:06:48,133 --> 00:06:51,333
我们做了一副新的漂亮的护目镜

472
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:55,066
但是这些和我们的鞋子不太相配

473
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:57,800
看了鞋子区后

474
00:06:57,833 --> 00:07:01,033
我们找不到任何适合新护目镜的东西

475
00:07:01,033 --> 00:07:05,133
所以我们改用电子魔法工具

476
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:09,000
这是只有贵宾才能使用的禁品

477
00:07:09,433 --> 00:07:11,300
既然我们已经够时髦了

478
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:12,900
我们可以获得更好的魔杖了

479
00:07:13,466 --> 00:07:15,900
我们很快升级了两次

480
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:18,533
但我们还不够满意

481
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:19,633
然而

482
00:07:19,633 --> 00:07:20,866
做一根更好的魔杖

483
00:07:20,866 --> 00:07:22,733
我们需要使用不同的路径

484
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,200
或者穿得更好

485
00:07:24,433 --> 00:07:28,033
虽然我们可以做更多很酷的电子魔法工具

486
00:07:28,033 --> 00:07:31,266
我们也许应该穿上正式的魔法师服装

487
00:07:31,466 --> 00:07:34,933
但这需要做太多的研究

488
00:07:35,533 --> 00:07:38,000
幸运的是，科技在这也能发挥作用

489
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,633
我们可以制造一台机器

490
00:07:39,633 --> 00:07:43,600
它将使用电力和节点为我们完成研究

491
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,866
我们所要做的就是

492
00:07:44,866 --> 00:07:46,133
输入一项研究笔记

493
00:07:46,133 --> 00:07:47,933
然后取出发现

494
00:07:48,233 --> 00:07:48,900
有了那个

495
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:51,700
我们可以研究所有可点击的内容

496
00:07:51,933 --> 00:07:52,666
然而

497
00:07:52,666 --> 00:07:57,433
做这么多研究实际上是在破坏这台机器使用的节点

498
00:07:57,533 --> 00:08:02,300
所以我们必须找到并带回一堆新的节点做更多的研究

499
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:06,000
这可能比手动进行所述研究需要更多时间

500
00:08:06,233 --> 00:08:10,433
我们在自然界中发现的弱节点也不会持续太久

501
00:08:10,666 --> 00:08:11,266
因此

502
00:08:11,266 --> 00:08:14,866
我们要找到人工创建节点的方法

503
00:08:15,033 --> 00:08:18,100
我们先制作一个节点基体(未调制)

504
00:08:18,733 --> 00:08:22,433
然后把所有没用的源质都喂给它

505
00:08:22,733 --> 00:08:25,466
最后将其注魔成一个节点

506
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,333
不过

507
00:08:26,333 --> 00:08:29,500
这个过程会使用太多的源质

508
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:32,533
所以我们必须找到更好的方法来融化物品

509
00:08:32,666 --> 00:08:36,133
大型源质冶炼厂似乎非常适合这项工作

510
00:08:36,333 --> 00:08:37,100
然而

511
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:40,100
我们遗漏了制作它所需的一些知识

512
00:08:40,533 --> 00:08:43,200
这些知识在魔法书的奇怪一页里

513
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,266
凭空出现的那种

514
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:49,300
里面的一切看起来都很怪异，似乎是禁忌

515
00:08:49,733 --> 00:08:52,600
但我们决定遵循那些奇怪的仪式

516
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,000
并加入邪教

517
00:08:54,133 --> 00:08:56,833
我们得到了一件漂亮的深色盔甲

518
00:08:57,033 --> 00:08:59,633
但我坚持认为白色的更好

519
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,600
这与持有反对意见的主教产生了争执

520
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:05,800
所以我们证明了自己的优越

521
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,000
然后把他关进监狱

522
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:10,733
直到他给我们一本关于所有禁忌仪式的秘籍

523
00:09:10,933 --> 00:09:14,066
然而我们越是触碰禁忌

524
00:09:14,066 --> 00:09:17,233
周围发生的怪事就越多

525
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:20,333
有时我们会被蜘蛛跟踪

526
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:22,333
有时是被 Arshog 跟踪

527
00:09:22,866 --> 00:09:25,866
而有时也被自己跟踪

528
00:09:26,233 --> 00:09:28,866
这很可能是工作太多造成的

529
00:09:28,866 --> 00:09:32,000
所以我们要在新的水疗中心休息一下

530
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,833
短暂休息之后

531
00:09:33,833 --> 00:09:36,333
是时候回去学习了

532
00:09:36,433 --> 00:09:38,466
但学的内容却越来越诡异

533
00:09:38,633 --> 00:09:41,200
我们现在陷得太深了

534
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,233
没有退路可言

535
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:46,533
禁书告诉我们的下一个任务是

536
00:09:46,533 --> 00:09:49,300
在被诅咒的祭坛上制造一个黑洞

537
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:51,600
我们在地图上见过那些祭坛

538
00:09:52,633 --> 00:09:54,000
沿着这条路走

539
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
我们到达黑暗领域

540
00:09:57,333 --> 00:10:00,700
在这个迷宫里游荡了一会儿后

541
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:02,533
我们发现了一扇奇怪的门

542
00:10:03,433 --> 00:10:06,500
幸运的是钥匙就在附近的房间里

543
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:09,633
只有几个虚弱的老鬼在保护它

544
00:10:10,433 --> 00:10:12,633
我们的磁铁很快就抓住了它

545
00:10:13,233 --> 00:10:14,266
有了这把钥匙

546
00:10:14,266 --> 00:10:16,400
我们打开那扇古老的门

547
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:20,233
在门后发现了一个可以承受我们

548
00:10:20,233 --> 00:10:23,633
碳十字弓发射的钒钢箭尖自动修复弩箭

549
00:10:23,633 --> 00:10:24,633
的 BOSS

550
00:10:25,033 --> 00:10:27,200
他还设法让我们陷入饥饿

551
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,933
对我们造成一些伤害

552
00:10:28,933 --> 00:10:30,833
所以我们打开量子护盾

553
00:10:30,833 --> 00:10:36,933
在跨纬度连接到此处的 AE 网络中寻找可口食物

554
00:10:37,433 --> 00:10:39,000
一旦我们吃饱了

555
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,733
我们拿下这个烦人的害虫

556
00:10:40,733 --> 00:10:44,233
甚至懒得从背包里掏出一把剑

557
00:10:44,866 --> 00:10:49,333
他给我们留下了升级冶炼厂需要的材料

558
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:53,633
然而，由于我们只有一颗珍珠

559
00:10:53,633 --> 00:10:56,666
我们将它种在一个空气清新的岛上

560
00:10:57,533 --> 00:11:00,900
然后我们用一些世界加速器来加速增长

561
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:03,200
看起来它长得太快了

562
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:07,233
作物监管机无法足够快地给它补水和施肥

563
00:11:09,033 --> 00:11:14,133
即使是 UV 作物管理器也跟不上加速后的作物

564
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,266
就在那时

565
00:11:16,266 --> 00:11:19,600
鬼魂来提醒我们从种田中休息一下

566
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,000
好好洗个澡

567
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:25,733
我们回来的时候正好看到珍珠绽放

568
00:11:27,300 --> 00:11:31,400
我们用它做出源质冶炼厂的缺失部分

569
00:11:32,033 --> 00:11:34,466
这个配方有些不稳定

570
00:11:34,466 --> 00:11:40,133
所以我们在祭坛上添加了一堆方块和装饰品来增加稳定性

571
00:11:40,866 --> 00:11:41,633
因此

572
00:11:41,633 --> 00:11:47,033
我们在制作新机器时设法将符文矩阵保持稳定

573
00:11:47,833 --> 00:11:49,866
但那只是控制器

574
00:11:50,033 --> 00:11:51,733
我们需要更多零件

575
00:11:52,433 --> 00:11:56,133
剩下的部分需要再注魔 20 次

576
00:11:56,133 --> 00:11:58,866
既然我们处在工业时代

577
00:11:58,866 --> 00:12:02,200
不应该像野蛮人一样注魔

578
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:06,233
SFM 可以管理工厂

579
00:12:06,233 --> 00:12:09,533
我猜它也能管理古代的仪式

580
00:12:10,666 --> 00:12:13,833
我们可以做一个关于如何设置这东西的教程

581
00:12:13,833 --> 00:12:16,866
但我认为这和我们的冒险不搭

582
00:12:16,866 --> 00:12:18,933
所以如果你想要教程

583
00:12:18,933 --> 00:12:21,000
在评论中提醒我

584
00:12:22,900 --> 00:12:25,866
无论如何，经过长时间的试错

585
00:12:25,866 --> 00:12:30,200
我们得到了 2 秒延迟的自动化注魔

586
00:12:31,066 --> 00:12:33,933
出于自动化程序本身的限制

587
00:12:33,933 --> 00:12:36,733
意味着每 4 秒注魔一次

588
00:12:37,733 --> 00:12:39,900
但这甚至不是一个完整的自动化

589
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:42,666
因为我们仍然需要手动管理源质

590
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:45,066
即使有更好的源质供给选择

591
00:12:46,266 --> 00:12:49,866
我们还要确保祭坛足够稳定

592
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:54,666
这个设置已经足够我们完成大型源质冶炼厂的制造了

593
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,866
它能以不错的速度工作

594
00:12:57,866 --> 00:12:59,666
但会产生相当多的咒波

595
00:13:00,733 --> 00:13:03,033
但我们可以通过多种方式升级它

596
00:13:03,033 --> 00:13:05,066
直到我们满意为止

597
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,333
现在我们只需要做很多点击

598
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:11,866
我想这可能会给我们一些扭曲

599
00:13:12,533 --> 00:13:16,100
不管怎样，一旦我们对点击感到厌烦

600
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:18,300
我们可以把它变成一个节点

601
00:13:18,633 --> 00:13:22,400
这将多用四倍已投入的源质

602
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:26,166
这意味着即使有 256 倍加速

603
00:13:26,166 --> 00:13:29,233
它仍然需要一些时间来完成注魔

604
00:13:29,666 --> 00:13:33,800
但至少现在我们可以坐着看

605
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,400
直到做出一个新节点

606
00:13:36,733 --> 00:13:39,133
我们将它用于研究

607
00:13:39,633 --> 00:13:42,433
那个节点很快就会用完

608
00:13:42,433 --> 00:13:47,100
但我认为它仍然比手动进行所有研究更容易

609
00:13:47,233 --> 00:13:49,600
另外，如果我们用得慢一点

610
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,033
可能有办法恢复节点

611
00:13:52,300 --> 00:13:55,266
这就是所有研究之后剩下的

612
00:13:55,433 --> 00:13:56,433
顺便说一下

613
00:13:56,433 --> 00:13:59,733
还有另一种方法可以使节点具有数百万要素

614
00:13:59,733 --> 00:14:01,733
但我不知道怎么搞

615
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:06,200
另外，我认为刚刚的过程给了我们点扭曲

616
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:09,666
现在是大扫除的好时机

617
00:14:09,833 --> 00:14:10,800
为此

618
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:12,633
我们只需要一滴纯净泪滴

619
00:14:13,033 --> 00:14:16,133
或者我们可以将其升级为被动配饰

620
00:14:16,533 --> 00:14:19,866
那东西会慢慢移除我们所有的扭曲

621
00:14:20,066 --> 00:14:22,200
让我们看看它有多快

622
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,600
在半个 Minecraft 日里

623
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,500
它完全没有消除永久扭曲

624
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,066
消除了一些一般扭曲

625
00:14:37,466 --> 00:14:41,500
当你有更多扭曲时，那东西应该更快

626
00:14:41,533 --> 00:14:43,733
我猜这需要太多时间

627
00:14:43,733 --> 00:14:45,466
所以让我们在这里使用它

628
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:49,833
它给我们带来了半个小时的各种效果

629
00:14:49,833 --> 00:14:53,800
厌倦于不知道会持续多久的等待

630
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:56,900
我们决定采取更快的方法

631
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:59,066
运气真好

632
00:14:59,066 --> 00:15:02,400
在最后一刻生成了一些凋零

633
00:15:02,533 --> 00:15:04,733
幸运的是，它们并没有困扰我们

634
00:15:04,733 --> 00:15:06,733
我们安全取回物品

635
00:15:06,733 --> 00:15:08,266
然后回去工作

636
00:15:08,566 --> 00:15:12,300
现在你可能想知道我们为什么要经历这一切

637
00:15:12,666 --> 00:15:13,233
好吧

638
00:15:13,233 --> 00:15:16,833
神秘限制了大量优质道具

639
00:15:16,933 --> 00:15:20,200
第一个是源质无线终端

640
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,233
用于制造通用终端

641
00:15:22,466 --> 00:15:26,300
这将允许我们从任何地方进行大量 AE 交互

642
00:15:26,833 --> 00:15:29,033
接下来是彩虹仙人掌

643
00:15:29,033 --> 00:15:31,533
我们可以制作无限喷漆罐

644
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:35,333
还可以制作心之容器

645
00:15:35,333 --> 00:15:36,700
这样我们就可以找出

646
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:39,266
生命条的下一个颜色是什么

647
00:15:39,666 --> 00:15:44,433
一些魔法相关的原版物品也需要神秘

648
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:47,300
某些仪式要求制作这些物品

649
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:49,300
用来激活一个古老的符印

650
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:55,033
你可能会想为什么我们要为那些古老的破碎的东西而经历围攻

651
00:15:55,133 --> 00:15:57,233
答案很简单

652
00:15:57,233 --> 00:15:58,933
过了这么多年

653
00:15:58,933 --> 00:16:03,266
我们想回答一个最古老的哲学问题

654
00:16:03,466 --> 00:16:05,600
答案很简单

655
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,266
过了这么多年

656
00:16:07,266 --> 00:16:11,700
我们想为最古老的数学问题之一找到答案

657
00:16:11,833 --> 00:16:14,500
用铁除以钻石能得到什么

658
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:17,800
答案似乎在薛定谔的猫身上

659
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,233
我们今天学的了什么？

660
00:16:20,466 --> 00:16:21,133
是呀

661
00:16:21,133 --> 00:16:24,766
再胡闹也要有 AE 帮我们兜底

662
00:02:23,433 --> 00:02:25,933
（奥数合成终端）

663
00:10:20,233 --> 00:10:24,633
（什么长难句）

664
00:12:16,866 --> 00:12:21,000
（原计划没有翻译这个教程，想看的也在评论弹幕提醒我）

665
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:17,800
（这锭处于稳定和不稳定的叠加态上）

